==English==
===Etymology===
From German ''[[Zugzwang]]'', litteraly "compulsion to move"
===Noun===
'''zugzwang''' (also '''Zugzwang''')
*{{chess}} A position in which one player is put at a disadvantage because he/she has to make a move.

